circularIf.#list.tail: v2 shows a more specific disjunction type with the recursive #list;
v3 evaluates to the concrete null default.
intField: v2 shows integer index fields 0 and 1 in result; v3 does not.
conflictRangingOverSelf.x.age: v2 reports position ./in.cue:39:5 but v3 does not.
